  \left[\begin{array}{c}2\\-3\\2\\-3\end{array}\right],
  \left[\begin{array}{c}1\\5\\-1\\0\end{array}\right]
  \right\}
  </m>.
        </p>
    </introduction>
  <task>
      <p>
    Mark the part of <m>\RREF\left[\begin{array}{cccc}
    2&amp;2&amp;2&amp;1\\
    3&amp;0&amp;-3&amp;5\\
    0&amp;1&amp;2&amp;-1\\
    1&amp;-1&amp;-3&amp;0
    \end{array}\right]</m> that shows that <m>W</m>'s spanning set
